Navigate through the surface of a hypersphere and kill your enemies.

* Necessary packages (used in Debian 6 and Ubuntu 11.04):
  build-essential
  automake (This and below only if you do not have "configure" script generated)
  autoconf
  libgl1-mesa-dev
  libglu1-mesa-dev
  libglew1.5-dev
  libsdl1.2-dev
  libboost-thread-dev >= 1.42
  libboost-system-dev >= 1.42
  libguichan-0.8.1-1
  libguichan-opengl-0.8.1-1
  libguichan-sdl-0.8.1-1
  libguichan-dev

* Optional packages:
  Doxygen

* Generate configuration files:
  $ autoreconf
  [ $ automake --add-missing ] (if necessary)
  $ automake -a -c (generate Makefiles)

* To change some macro (m4):
  $ aclocal
  -> generate configuration files again
  -> standard procedure

* Compile:
  $ ./configure
  $ make

* Generate documentation:
  $ make doxygen-doc

* Play:
  $ cd src
  $ ./navigna
